description: The 2024 Lincoln Navigator L Reserve in Flight Blue Metallic is the ultimate expression of American luxury and space. This ""L"" model features an extended wheelbase, providing significantly more cargo room behind the third row compared to the standard Navigator. The Black Onyx leather interior is designed as a ""sanctuary,"" featuring high-end wood accents and a massive touchscreen that serves as the hub for the vehicle's many comfort and entertainment systems.Under the hood, this Navigator is powered by a high-output twin-turbocharged V6 engine that offers effortless power and smooth acceleration, even when fully loaded with passengers. Its intelligent 4WD system and adaptive suspension work together to glide over road imperfections, maintaining a quiet and composed ride.At Galpin Ford, our commitment to our customers produces one of the most valuable assets and that's trust! We know you can't buy trust. You have to earn it! People have come to know that they can trust Galpin for the right selection, the right price, the right service and the latest innovations. That's why 92% of our customers are either repeat, reputational or referral. That's the Power of Trust! With over 75 years of automotive excellence we offer a commitment to an open, honest, and fair shopping experience. As an auto group we represent over 12 different brands from Volkswagen, Mazda, Honda, Lotus, Ford, Land Rover, Aston Martin, Lincoln, Polestar and Volvo. We have done a great amount of work to have the perfect selection of Pre-Owned vehicles and have researched hundreds of dealerships within a set radius to ensure we are competitively priced. Come on in today to check out our selection of Pre-Owned vehicles and experience exceptional service you can trust! Call or Visit us   .

Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance with this stunning 2024 Porsche Cayenne Base. Crafted with the precision and attention to detail that Porsche is renowned for, this SUV is the perfect blend of power, sophistication, and versatility.

Turn heads with this exceptionally rare and beautifully appointed 2014 BMW 428i Coupe in one of the most sought-after color combinations: Sparkling Brown Metallic exterior paired with rich Dakota Saddle Brown leather interior. This eye-catching metallic brown shines with depth and elegance, complemented by the warm, premium saddle leather that gives the cabin a luxurious, upscale feel few 4-Series examples can match.

Luxury Line package with premium touches throughout
18" alloy wheels wrapped in luxury all-season tires
Anthracite wood trim + rare Highlight trim finishers in pearl gloss
Power-adjustable front seats with heating

Must see and test drive to appreciate the condition and that gorgeous color combo in person!
